{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/react-setting","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"b58f308e-7244-5de5-a37a-8683c2368ccf","html":"<p>react.js로 프로젝트를 해본적은 없다.<br>\n처음에 vue.js로 작업을 진행했을 때는 신기하고 너무 편했다.<br>\n이후로 react에 대한 관심도 많아졌다.\nvue cli 처럼 cra(create-react-app)라는 보일러플레이트가 있다.<br>\nvue cli는 참 편하게 사용했으니 CRA를 이용해서 한번 해볼까 하다가<br>\n삽질일지도 모르겠지만 그냥 아무것도 없는 상태에서 세팅을 해보자라는 생각을 했다.<br>\n저번달에 이미 해봤지만 기억이 잘 안나는 관계로 다시 진행해보려한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"npm-init\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#npm-init\" aria-label=\"npm init permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>npm init</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm init -y</code></pre></div>\n<p>명령어를 입력하면 package.json이 생성된다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"webpack\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#webpack\" aria-label=\"webpack permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>webpack</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save-dev webpack webpack-dev-server webpack-cli\nor\nyarn add -D webpack webpack-dev-server webpack-cli</code></pre></div>\n<p>webpack.config.js 파일을 만들어주고 아래 내용을 추가한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">const path = require(&quot;path&quot;);\nconst HtmlWebpackPlugin = require(&quot;html-webpack-plugin&quot;);\n\nmodule.exports = {\n  mode: &quot;development&quot;,\n\n  entry: &quot;./src/index&quot;,\n\n  resolve: {\n    extensions: [&quot;.js&quot;, &quot;.jsx&quot;]\n  },\n\n  module: {\n    rules: [\n      {\n        test: /\\.jsx?$/,\n        loader: &quot;babel-loader&quot;,\n        exclude: /node_modules/\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  output: {\n    path: path.resolve(__dirname, &quot;dist&quot;),\n    filename: &quot;bundle.[hash].js&quot;\n  },\n  devServer: {\n    historyApiFallback: true,\n    open: false,\n    port: 8080,\n    host: &#39;localhost&#39;,\n    hot: true,\n    inline: true\n  },\n  plugins: [\n    new HtmlWebpackPlugin({\n      template: `./public/index.html`\n    })\n  ]\n};</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"babel\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#babel\" aria-label=\"babel permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Babel</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add -D @babel/core @babel/preset-env @babel/preset-react babel-loader</code></pre></div>\n<p>babel.config.js 파일을 만든 뒤 아래 내용을 추가한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">module.exports = function(api) {\n  api.cache(true);\n\n  const presets = [&quot;@babel/preset-env&quot;, &quot;@babel/preset-react&quot;];\n\n  const plugins = [];\n\n  return {\n    presets,\n    plugins\n  };\n};</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"react\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#react\" aria-label=\"react permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>react</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add react react-dom</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"public-폴더에-indexhtml을-만들어준다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#public-%ED%8F%B4%EB%8D%94%EC%97%90-indexhtml%EC%9D%84-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EC%A4%80%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"public 폴더에 indexhtml을 만들어준다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>public 폴더에 index.html을 만들어준다.</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\n&lt;html lang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;head&gt;\n    &lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot; /&gt;\n    &lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot; /&gt;\n    &lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;X-UA-Compatible&quot; content=&quot;ie=edge&quot; /&gt;\n    &lt;title&gt;Document&lt;/title&gt;\n  &lt;/head&gt;\n  &lt;body&gt;\n    &lt;div id=&quot;root&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"src-폴더에-indexjs를-만든다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#src-%ED%8F%B4%EB%8D%94%EC%97%90-indexjs%EB%A5%BC-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A0%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"src 폴더에 indexjs를 만든다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>src 폴더에 index.js를 만든다.</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import React from &quot;react&quot;;\nimport ReactDOM from &quot;react-dom&quot;;\nimport App from &quot;./components/App&quot;;\n\nReactDOM.render(&lt;App /&gt;, document.getElementById(&quot;#root&quot;));</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"components-폴더에-appjs를-만든다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#components-%ED%8F%B4%EB%8D%94%EC%97%90-appjs%EB%A5%BC-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A0%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"components 폴더에 appjs를 만든다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>components 폴더에 App.js를 만든다.</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import React from &quot;react&quot;;\n\nconst App = () =&gt; {\n  return &lt;div&gt;hello world!&lt;/div&gt;;\n};\nexport default App;</code></pre></div>\n<p>리액트는 함수나 클래스로 작성한다.<br>\n실제로 프로젝트를 진행하면서 정리해보겠다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"스크립트-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"스크립트 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>스크립트 추가</h4>\n<p>package.json scripts에 아래 내용을 추가한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&quot;build&quot;: &quot;webpack&quot;,\n&quot;watch&quot;: &quot;webpack-dev-server --inline --hot&quot;\n\nyarn build\nyarn watch</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"scss\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#scss\" aria-label=\"scss permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>scss</h4>\n<p>css 보다 편하다.<br>\nscss 설정을 해보자!   </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add -D node-sass style-loader sass-loader css-loader</code></pre></div>\n<p>webpack.config.js에 설정을 추가한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n    test: /\\.(css|scss)$/,\n    use: [\n        &#39;style-loader&#39;,\n        &#39;css-loader&#39;,\n        {\n        loader: &#39;sass-loader&#39;,\n        options: {\n            sassOptions:{\n            includePaths: [`${__dirname}/src/scss`],\n            },\n            prependData: `@import &#39;/utilities/variables&#39;;`\n        }\n        }\n    ]\n    },</code></pre></div>\n<p>css-loader는 외부에서 css를 import한 경우 에러가 발생하여 추가했다.<br>\n각 파일을 해당 컴포넌트에 import하면 문서내 style tag로 들어간다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add -D mini-css-extract-plugin</code></pre></div>\n<p>별도로 css파일을 만들어주는 플러그인이다.<br>\nwebpack.config.js에 아래와 같이 추가해주자!</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">const MiniCssExtractPlugin = require(&#39;mini-css-extract-plugin&#39;);\n\n{\n    test: /\\.(css|scss)$/,\n    use: [\n        MiniCssExtractPlugin.loader,\n    ]\n},\nplugins: [\n    new MiniCssExtractPlugin({ filename: &#39;/src/css/app.[hash].css&#39;,})\n]</code></pre></div>\n<p>postcss-loader 는 나중에 추가해보도록 한다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"clean-webpack-plugin\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#clean-webpack-plugin\" aria-label=\"clean webpack plugin permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>clean-webpack-plugin</h4>\n<p>build를 하게 되면 이전에 묶였던 파일들이 그대로 남아있다.<br>\n매번 삭제하기 번거로우니 추가해주도록 하자.<br>\n알아서 삭제해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add -D clean-webpack-plugin\n\nconst { CleanWebpackPlugin } = require(&#39;clean-webpack-plugin&#39;);\n\nplugins: [\nnew CleanWebpackPlugin({\n    cleanAfterEveryBuildPatterns: [&#39;dist&#39;]\n}),</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"router\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#router\" aria-label=\"router permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>router</h4>\n<p>vue.js는 공식 라우터가 있다.<br>\nreact는 서드파티 라이브러리를 사용해야한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add react-router-dom</code></pre></div>\n<p>사용 예시    </p>\n<h5 id=\"appjs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#appjs\" aria-label=\"appjs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>app.js</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import { BrowserRouter } from &#39;react-router-dom&#39;;\n\n&lt;div className=&quot;wrap&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;BrowserRouter&gt;\n        &lt;Header /&gt;\n        &lt;Routes /&gt;\n    &lt;/BrowserRouter&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<h5 id=\"headerjs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#headerjs\" aria-label=\"headerjs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Header.js</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import { Link } from &#39;react-router-dom&#39;;\n&lt;header&gt;\n    &lt;ul&gt;\n        &lt;li&gt;\n            &lt;Link to=&quot;/&quot;&gt;main&lt;/Link&gt;\n        &lt;/li&gt;\n        &lt;li&gt;\n            &lt;Link to=&quot;/about&quot;&gt;About&lt;/Link&gt;\n        &lt;/li&gt;\n    &lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;/header&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<h5 id=\"routesjs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#routesjs\" aria-label=\"routesjs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Routes.js</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import { Route, Switch } from &quot;react-router-dom&quot;;\n&lt;main&gt;\n    &lt;Switch&gt;\n        &lt;Route exact path=&quot;/&quot; component={Main} /&gt;\n        &lt;Route path=&quot;/about&quot; component={About} /&gt;\n    &lt;/Switch&gt;\n&lt;/main&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p>BrowserRouter가 감싸고 그 안에 Link로 이동할 주소를 설정한다.<br>\nRoute, Switch는 해당 주소에서 선택된 component를 보여준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&quot;dependencies&quot;: {\n    &quot;react&quot;: &quot;^16.13.0&quot;,\n    &quot;react-dom&quot;: &quot;^16.13.0&quot;,\n    &quot;react-router-dom&quot;: &quot;^5.1.2&quot;\n},\n&quot;devDependencies&quot;: {\n    &quot;@babel/core&quot;: &quot;^7.8.6&quot;,\n    &quot;@babel/preset-env&quot;: &quot;^7.8.6&quot;,\n    &quot;@babel/preset-react&quot;: &quot;^7.8.3&quot;,\n    &quot;babel-loader&quot;: &quot;^8.0.6&quot;,\n    &quot;clean-webpack-plugin&quot;: &quot;^3.0.0&quot;,\n    &quot;css-loader&quot;: &quot;^3.4.2&quot;,\n    &quot;html-webpack-plugin&quot;: &quot;^3.2.0&quot;,\n    &quot;mini-css-extract-plugin&quot;: &quot;^0.9.0&quot;,\n    &quot;node-sass&quot;: &quot;^4.13.1&quot;,\n    &quot;postcss-flexbugs-fixes&quot;: &quot;^4.2.0&quot;,\n    &quot;postcss-loader&quot;: &quot;^3.0.0&quot;,\n    &quot;postcss-preset-env&quot;: &quot;^6.7.0&quot;,\n    &quot;sass-loader&quot;: &quot;^8.0.2&quot;,\n    &quot;style-loader&quot;: &quot;^1.1.3&quot;,\n    &quot;url-loader&quot;: &quot;^3.0.0&quot;,\n    &quot;webpack&quot;: &quot;^4.42.0&quot;,\n    &quot;webpack-cli&quot;: &quot;^3.3.11&quot;,\n    &quot;webpack-dev-server&quot;: &quot;^3.10.3&quot;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"절대경로-바벨-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%88%EB%8C%80%EA%B2%BD%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B0%94%EB%B2%A8-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"절대경로 바벨 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>절대경로 바벨 설정</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add -D babel-plugin-module-resolver</code></pre></div>\n<p>babel.config.js</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">const plugins = [\n  [&quot;module-resolver&quot;, {\n    // &quot;root&quot;: [&quot;./src&quot;],\n    &quot;alias&quot;: {\n      &quot;@&quot;: &quot;./src&quot;\n    }\n  }]\n];</code></pre></div>\n<p>플러그인 추가하면 ../../ 등의 복잡한 경로를 쓸 필요가 없다!!</p>\n<h3 id=\"env\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#env\" aria-label=\"env permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>.env</h3>\n<p>환경변수 설정</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add -D dotenv-webpack</code></pre></div>\n<p>webpack.config.js</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">const Dotenv = require(&#39;dotenv-webpack&#39;);\n...\nnew Dotenv({\n  path: &#39;./.env&#39;, // load this now instead of the ones in &#39;.env&#39;\n  safe: true, // load &#39;.env.example&#39; to verify the &#39;.env&#39; variables are all set. Can also be a string to a different file.\n  systemvars: true, // load all the predefined &#39;process.env&#39; variables which will trump anything local per dotenv specs.\n  silent: true, // hide any errors\n  defaults: false // load &#39;.env.defaults&#39; as the default values if empty.\n}),</code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/react-setting","tagSlugs":["/tag/library/","/tag/react/","/tag/web-development/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-03-03","description":"CRA없이 리액트 세팅해보기","tags":["library","react","Web Development"],"title":"리액트 세팅해보기( without CRA )","socialImage":"/bg_work.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/react-setting"}}}